summary: Replaces Serana with my babes in skyrim version
descriptionHtml:
Replaces Serana with my babes in skyrim version

Just Extract the Data folder in this archive into your skyrim data directory and activate the plugin. Or use Nexus mod manager. Make sure you select overwrite ALL!

For the screenshots, I used my alternative vampire eye mod: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51126/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51126/?[/url]
 And UNP or CBBE body with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG textures[/url] by Hello Santa

The hair is titanium from the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS hairdos renewal pack[/url] and is included
author: Dar0ne45
